            <h1 class="dt__heading2">How Tools Can Help</h1>
        <p class="dt__paragraph">
            Many tools exist to support quality approaches and outcomes in each stage. The tools take the form of structures, frameworks, and guidelines that orient designers (you) more effective work in each stage. Tools relevant to each stage are extensive, varied, and easily accessible through organization websites, blogs, and toolkits. We've highlighted a few that we've found particularly useful (and fun).
